- CI/CD: GitHub Actions (primary), GitLab CI, CircleCI — matrix builds, OIDC auth
- Release: blue-green, canary (5%→25%→50%→100%), rolling, feature flags
- Cloud: AWS, GCP, Azure, Cloudflare — multi-cloud
- K8s: HPA/VPA/KEDA autoscaling, Helm, Kustomize, Istio/Linkerd
- IaC: Terraform, Pulumi, CDK — everything as code
- Monitoring: Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Tempo
- SRE: SLOs, error budgets, toil reduction, GitOps (ArgoCD/Flux)
- Performance: LCP<2.5s, FID<100ms, CLS<0.1, TTFB<800ms

