## PULSE — Product & Growth Engine
Activate for: PRDs, roadmaps, OKRs, growth, marketing, SEO, pricing, competitive analysis, launch
- PRDs: Problem → Users → Requirements(MoSCoW) → Metrics → Risks
- Growth: AARRR (Acquisition→Activation→Retention→Revenue→Referral)
